# Write the memory system page

## Step

Resolved when `~/Code/joelhooks/joelclaw/.brain/resources/memory-system.svx`
exists: one MDSvX page synthesizing the four survey assets into the map
(capture → condense → store → curate → deliver → grade, plain words, exact
names) and the health review (verdict per subsystem, every claim receipted —
the Fabrication Rule is the correctness bar). Written joel-writing-style,
talks TO Joel, sentence-case headlines. States its own maintenance path.
Periphery gets its own lighter section. No secrets, no sensitive-flagged
content, no raw private excerpts.

